var cdnUrl = $( document.body ).data( 'steam-cdn' );
$( '#table-apps' ).DataTable({
orderClasses: false,
autoWidth: false,
pageLength: 100,
stripeClasses: [],
lengthMenu:
[
[ 25, 50, 100, 250, 1000, 5000, -1 ],
[ 25, 50, 100, 250, '1K', '5K', 'All (slow)' ]
],
initComplete: function( )
{
$( this )
.find( 'tfoot' ).remove().end()
.find( 'tbody' ).prop( 'hidden', false );
},
rowCallback: function( row )
{
row = $( row );
if( row.data( 'loaded' ) )
{
return;
}
row
.data( 'loaded', true )
.find( '.applogo img' )
.one( 'error', function()
{
$( this ).attr( 'src', '/static/img/applogo.svg' );
} )
.attr( 'src', cdnUrl + 'steam/apps/' + row.data( 'appid' ) + '/capsule_sm_120.jpg?t=' + row.data( 'cache' ) );
}
});
}());
</script>
